{"tid":313008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港亞協禁黃之鋒演講　美總部稱震驚","createTime":"2017-07-08T03:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T13:31:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6d961108a681bf2593559cbd32ee5e421f71a0","tid":313008,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20082764&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20082764%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170708&d=u2iZjVnb%2BmtcLs3ACRVQ4%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=3a73213e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20082764%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170708&h=6ece700c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20082764&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170708</a><br />\n<br />\n港亞協禁黃之鋒演講　美總部稱震驚<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由「梁粉」恒隆集團董事長陳啟宗任主席的亞洲協會香港中心，上月疑因政治理由，拒絕借出場地予香港筆會舉行新書發佈會，原因是眾志秘書長黃之鋒將在會上發言。總部在紐約的亞洲協會美中關係中心發聲明，對香港中心做法感震驚，又重申協會宗旨是支持公開的思想交流。<br />\n香港筆會較早前出版以回歸20周年為主題新書《Hong Kong20/20: Reflections on a borrowed place》，黃之鋒是作者之一。<br />\n<br />\n眾志：無補救措施感失望<br />\n<br />\n香港筆會原定在位於金鐘的亞洲協會香港中心舉行新書發佈會。但中心上月通知筆會，要求黃之鋒不能在發佈會上發言，活動最終要改往另一地點進行。<br />\n亞洲協會美中關係中心昨發表聲明指出，對香港中心禁止黃之鋒在新書發佈會上發言的報道感震驚。<br />\n中心重申該會宗旨一直是致力於各種思想開放交流，言論自由是工作重點，促進中美兩國就不同意見的相互了解。香港眾志發表聲明回應，對於亞洲協會領導沒有作出補救措施表示失望。<br />\n■記者麥志榮"},{"pid":"c4bc8420b3093260fb432611b928242577561b86","tid":313008,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bcdd8a2867f4e0ae70eac17a986a8ad35fa4547","tid":313008,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:47:32.000Z","msg":"打壓無處不在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b221f932447268fa6e4b50074a50220e507f54","tid":313008,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩，美國好惡<br />\n<br />\n老細唔鐘意做你生意就唔做<br />\n在商言商，有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n又唔係全港封殺</blockquote><br />\n等我叫連囝bam你條柒頭皮先<br />\n在商言商 唔好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5d0cae258282e43e4f21a3d75cf5f260113b62","tid":313008,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}